headline: Lennar Debuts North River Farms in Oceanside, CA
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, today announced the grand opening of North River Farms, a new master-planned community of single-family homes in Oceanside, CA. Offering 17 distinct home designs, North River Farms delivers a highly-amenitized setting with an unparalleled lifestyle. Interested homebuyers are invited to tour the new model homes and take advantage of special grand opening incentives. The celebration is on Saturday, August 23 at 11:00 a.m.
